### Link to this sectionSemanticMask#

`SemanticMask` stores one dense class map for semantic segmentation results. Unlike `Masks`, it does not contain one binary mask per object and does not provide polygon helpers.

SemanticMask
    
    
    from ultralytics import YOLO
    
    # Load a pretrained YOLO26n-sem Semantic model
    model = YOLO("yolo26n-sem.pt")
    
    # Run inference on an image
    results = model("https://ultralytics.com/images/bus.jpg")  # results list
    
